### Installing Argocd Helm Chart by overriding the parameters related to argocd-server service and changing it from ClusterIP type to NodePort

### Install Argocd Helm Chart as following:
kubectl create ns argocd
helm repo add argo https://argoproj.github.io/argo-helm
helm install argocd argo/argo-cd -n argocd -f installation/helm/values.yaml
exposing via port forward : kubectl port-forward svc/argocd-server 8089:80
kubectl alias : Set-Alias k kubectl
